1. *Ostajem* da čekam tvoj odgovor. (I'll stay to wait for your answer.)
2. Mislim da ću *ostati* kod kuće. (I think I will stay at home.)
3. Ne treba mi ništa, *ostaću* sam. (I don't need anything, I'll stay alone.)
4. Trenutno *ostajemo* na istom mestu. (We are currently staying in the same place.)
5. *Ostaju* nam još neka pitanja. (We still have some questions remaining.)